  "body": "zkSync gets L2 key from a signature: https://github.com/matter-labs/zksync/blob/5b936b1855a08033cca7f75d6f87fde106c6e8fd/sdk/zksync.js/src/signer.ts#L235-L255\r\n\r\nHowever, ECDSA is a non-deterministic scheme and signature result may be different every time.\r\n\r\nThis means an user need to be careful: if she/he loses her/his zksync wallet, she/he will be hard to re-produce the L2 key? \r\n\r\nThough she/he can still force exit from L1.",
